commit.message:
ENH: Support user categories in OneHotEncoder (#727)

* ENH: Support user categories in OneHotEncoder

Allows for

```python
ohe = OneHotEncoder(categories=[['a', 'b'], ['c', 'd']])
```

Previously, we required inputs to be CategoricalDtype for dataframes.

Closes https://github.com/dask/dask-ml/issues/726

* bump minimum
